image.caption: Black clouds hang over the Bangabandhu national stadium in Dhaka

milestones.description: Aasif Karim has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Martin Suji's 4
Grant Flower has broken the record for most catches (38) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Campbell's 37
Aasif Karim has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (25) for KENYA, going past Hitesh Modi
Zimbabwe's 203-run win against Kenya is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 192-run win against Bangladesh
